pull_request.body:

- [ ] Need AES CTR mode
- [ ] Doesn't yet have Streamlined NTRU
- [ ] Not yet merged into PQClean; see note added to the ntruprime algorithm datasheet for details.

pull_request.title: Add SPHINCS+ from PQClean
pull_request.body:
This PR adds all SPHINCS+ signature schemes from PQClean.

I have some scripts that generated the major files, I don't suggest maintaining any of these files by hand. (Where) should I store those?

Also adds an incremental hashing API to FIPS202 and adds SHA2 + the accompanying pqclean shims.

Closes #482

pull_request.title: Add SPHINCS+ from PQClean
pull_request.body:
Fixes #482.  Replaces #483.

Still need to add SHA256 variants; this will involve adding a SHA-2 API & implementation to liboqs.  

The Haraka and SHA256 variants in PQClean are currently not thread-safe; see https://github.com/PQClean/PQClean/issues/168.  This should not be merged into liboqs until that issue is resolved.
